<div>
    <center><h1 id="About">About Project</h1></center>
    <p>
                        One of the common causes of senility in the elderly and obese is osteoarthritis.
         A joint condition called  osteoarthritis attacks the cartilage in larger joints like the knee, hip, foot, and spine. 
         Bones slide More easily over cartilage, which prevents them from scraping against one another. Osteoarthritis causes cartilage to break, which causes the bones to begin rubbing against one another in extreme pain. 
         Doctor may prescribe painkillers such acetaminophen, nonsteroidal anti-inflammatory medicines like aspirin, ibuprofen, or naproxen, or even narcotics.
         But long-term use of these drugs can lead . Doctor wants to treat the osteoarthritis in the knee with surgery ,the options are arthroscopy , osteotomy and arthroplasty.
         The user(patient) want to register their name and an id will be given to them , using that id they can submit their report and view the doctor.
        To the user view home-page will be created and both the Doctor and User will have their own login id’s.When the report is submitted to the doctor ,the report get scanned/compared with the stored report .
         This process takes place at the back-side of this application. By using this application the user(patient) can generate their report’s result.
        By getting their report they comes to know about their problem and by viewing doctor they can take their medicine properly. </p>  
    </p>
    <h2>2.1 Project Description</h2>
    <p>
        KOD is an simple and friendly medical application . 
        This is an useful application foe those person got fractured and got their scan report , but insufficient to visit the hospital and know their outcome of the report from the doctor .
         Those persons are allowed to use this app -lication and know their report outcome just being at home itself . 
         This application provide  facilities to view the doctor and query their questions to the doctor . 
         In our project Admin is the major role , who is the intermediate between doctor and the user . Login page is available for the admin , using their login id they can login .
         In admin  page there some facilities like view-doctor, view-scan,…....The doctors are allowed to see the report through the view-scan option and the patient are able to visit is the doctor using viewdoctor .
         Admin page is being home page for both doctors and users. Here doctor first want to login into their page through admin’s home page .
          Main job of the doctors is to visit into the view scan page and check the scan report and suggest the patient what they want to do next and suggest them the medicine to be taken . 
          There is another job for the doctors to do ,they want to visit view-query page and give a replay to the queries asked by the patient . 
         User first want to register their details and then they can login to the application . 
         Then user want to submit their scan report using add-scan option .
         After adding their report , they can visit into the doctors page using view-doctor option , and know the result of their report . 
         If patients have any question they can review their queries to doctor through add-query page .
    </p>
</div></section>
