<div>
    <center><h1 id="sst">System Study</h1></center>
    <p>
       <h3>System study is classified into two types</h3> 
        <ul><li>Existing system</li>  
	        <li>Proposed system </li>
    </p>
    <h2>2.3 Existing System :</h2>
        <p>
            In the existing concept if  anyone patient got injured want to take a scan and visit the for away/near by hospital .
            In that case it is not safe for the patient to travel with the pain.
            Sometime the doctors may not present at the hospital , due to that they may want to visit another hospital or come back to home with pain without any solution for that pain. Even Some times their won’t be any proper treatments and proper instruction.
            And Sometime doctors may not answer our queries. 
        </p>
    <h2>2.4 Proposed System : </h2>
    <p>
        In the proposed system the user can use this application to know their report result with short time interval .
         The user want to register their name and an id will be given to them . 
         By using their id they can login to submit their scanned report . 
         Once the report is submitted the report get scanned and move on to the doctors view point . 
         Then the user can view the doctor  to know their problem in their knee . 
         The doctors also provide proper medicine and tips to recover their pain and come  back to normal form.
         User may have some doubt about their description  and they can text queries and get the proper answer from the doctors. 
    </p>
  </div>
 </section>
